'''Tasnusit''' (neɣ '''Tamaziɣt n Ayt Snus''') tga yat tntala tamaziɣt nna bahra yaẓn i [[tutlayin tiznatiyin]] ittusawaln ɣ iwttayn n Tlmsan ɣ Dzayr<ref>-{Souag, Lameen (2009-03-19). "[http://lughat.blogspot.com/2009/03/beni-snous-two-unrelated-phonetic-forms.html Beni-Snous: Two unrelated phonetic forms for every noun?]". ''Jabal al-Lughat''. Retrieved 2010-01-08.}-</ref><ref>-{Ilahiane, Hsain (2006). [https://books.google.com/books?id=0E8qp_k515oC&pg=PA84 Historical dictionary of the Berbers (Imazighen).] Rowman & Littlefield. p. 84. <nowiki>ISBN 978-0-8108-5452-9</nowiki>.}-</ref><ref>-{"[http://www.centrederechercheberbere.fr/snous.html Centre de Recherche Berbère - Beni Snous]". ''www.centrederechercheberbere.fr'' (in French). Retrieved 2017-07-21.}-</ref>.

Tkka-tt-inn tutlayt-ad ar tettusawal ɣ iduwwarn n Kef, Tɣalimt, Bu Hallu, Ayt lɛṛbi, Ayt Acir, Adziddaz d Mazzr ɣ tezwiri n tasuta tiss 20<ref>-{Destaing, Edmond (1907). ''Etude sur le dialecte berbère des Beni-Snous''. Paris: Ernest Leroux. p. XXVIII.}-</ref>; gin akkʷ imsawaln si-s isinutlayn s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|teɛṛabt]]. Ayt Suns kkan-tt-inn ur da ttafan amukris ɣ umsawaḍ d waddjaṛn-nnsn imslmaziɣn n Ayt bu sɛid f utaram-nnsn, iẓḍuṛn ula ad msawḍn (mqqar d s ccqawt) d imslmaziɣn n [[Ayt iznasn|Ayt Iznasn]] d [[Figig]]. Maccan, ggamin ad fhmn amya ɣ [[Tutlayt Taclḥit|Tcelḥit]] (anẓul n [[lmɣrib]]) d [[Tutlayt Taqbaylit|Tqbaylit]] (Agafa n [[Dzayr]]).

Ass-a, middn imqqurn ka ad sul issnn i tmaziɣt. Amata n Ayt Snus mmatin s teɛṛabt, amẓn ɣar mnnawt tguriwin zɣ tutlayt n iqburn-nnsn, zun d tabɣa (blackberries) neɣ adzduz (pestle)<ref>-{Souag, Lameen; Kherbache, Fatma (9 June 2014). "[https://halshs.archives-ouvertes.fr/halshs-01376208/file/postprint-souag_kherbache_2016_syntactically_conditioned_code-switching.pdf Syntactically conditioned code-switching? The syntax of numerals in Beni-Snous Berber]" (PDF). International Journal of Bilingualism. SAGE. '''18''' (4): 97–115. doi:[[doi:10.1177/1367006914536002|10.1177/1367006914536002]]. ISSN [[issn:1756-6878|1756-6878]]. S2CID [https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:144281357 144281357].}-</ref>.

